title: FS2004 - Cloud9 Amsterdam scenery v1.01 (crack ONLY)
description:
VERIFIED

Cloud9's Amsterdam scenery - Welkom op Schiphol (CRACK ONLY)

http://www.fscloud9.com/php/products.php?lang=EN&id=78

For those amongst you already having the Amsterdam scenery (v1.01) installer, here's just the crack needed to install this great add-on.

Many thanks to GoLeafs for sending me this fine add-on.
All credits go to him and to Wildmans (the writer of the crack)!!!

One little note: the add-ons will continue to function after the 5 minutes time-limit, however I did see some "old" scenery shimmering through at one point. It could have been my somewhat older videocard though, but please report any of such problems if they might occur.


Happy Dutch Going,
